    java.lang.Runnable

    public class LeveledDecisionTree
extends BasicDecisionTree
    LeveledDecisionTree takes in a number and uses that to base the difficulty of the ai. there are really only 4 settings:
    • Good at nothing
    • 1 Skill
    • 2 Skill
    • All 3 Skill
    With the skills being shooting, shielding, and movement. The skills are randomly selected.
    Author:
    Max Knutsen - mknutse1@umbc.edu
